# Episodic event log

Append-only JSONL files. Satisfies Kernel Rule 22 (epistemic transparency).

## Format

One JSON object per line. Required fields:

```json
{
  "timestamp": "<ISO 8601>",
  "agent": "<agent-name>",
  "project": "<project-name>",
  "action": "<action-type>",
  "confidence": 0.0,
  "sources": ["..."],
  "constitutional_check": "Passed Rule N",
  "kernel_version": "v6"
}
```

See [`../../layers/L6-observability.md`](../../layers/L6-observability.md) for the full schema.

## Retention

Default: 90 days hot, then compress and archive (§H Q7).

Files rotate when they exceed 10 MB or at midnight UTC, whichever comes first.

Actual log files are gitignored — they're an audit artifact, not a versioned artifact.
